dmca.title: Cease and Desist
dmca.body:
You are using my name to cause me and my family trouble. You have used it in the past to threaten me and my family and you have attempted to call my landlord by leaving messages on the phone at the security desk.
You use my name to negativity and defamation to my famous name. My name is a trademark and you are causing confusion with my business. Your intention are negative. I am demanding that you cease and desist using my name in your URL,titles of your blog and do not have any reference to me or my family. You are hurting my business. Stop now
